Own Choice Test Piece Contest
Värnamo, Småland, Sweden The Swedish Brass Band Association have decided that this years nationals will only have a testpiece in the elite division. The first and second division will only have an own choice program of maximum 25 minutes. The decision comes with the unsure conditions with the bands posibillities to prepare for the contest during the Covid-19 restrictions.
